2:04 PM Defendant Diana L Graveen appeared by video, in custody from the Vilas County Jail.  Attorney Karl Peter Hayes in court for State of Wisconsin. Defendant confirms receipt of the criminal complaint. Court reads charges. Attorney rights given. Ms Graveen will be contacting the public defenders office. State speaks to bond. Court issues $1,000 signature bond with conditions: No driving without a valid license, no contact with TT (1991), JM(1992), WB(1968), Not to possess, use, or ingest illegal drugs. Bond form.
